headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Krose GmbH & Co KG
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Bremen, Germany-based Krose GmbH & Co KG ("Krose"). Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
